data.text: Yoooo I remember when covid first started and it was announced that Rudy gobert had it at the NBA game in Indiana & that shit was wild now the day of the trade deadline for NBA cali & New York lifted the vaccine / mask mandate  this country is a joke
Avian turkey flu in indiana?  Ya sure this plandemic isn’t going anywhere they will keep coming up with different variants till 100% vaccination which means never ends
So I get a msg and email from the Indiana Dept of Health inviting me to have a COVID vaccine.    I sent them back a BIG 🖕

Lincoln National Insurance death claims have skyrocketed 57% since vaccine release. Prudential is up 41%. 2 weeks ago the CEO of an Indiana based insurance company stated their's were up over 40% and for comparison said a 1 in 200 year catastrophe would only cause a 10% increase.
Just a brutal day for #KnicksTwitter…first we see Halliburton go to Indiana which means no Fox. And now NY is about to end vaccine mandate indoors tomorrow so #Nets gettin #Kyrie back full time 😐

#Indiana is suppose to have a lot of Christians.  One of the reasons I relocated here.  You would never know it with the mask/vaccine mandates?  Not using the intelligence Jesus gave us?  Are @GovHolcomb and @AGToddRokita men of faith?
